Package: Records
Type: Package
Title: Record-count Statistics for Multiple Stochastic Models
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Jinane", "Jouni", , "jinane.jouni@hotmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0007-7150-9065"))
Description: Compute expected number of records, variance and exact/count distribution of
    record counts under several models (IID, DTRW, LDM, YNM). Includes a registry-based
    dispatcher and utilities to extend with new models.
